1
00:00:10,267 --> 00:00:13,498
- Mr Silverstein?
- Yes. Who are you?
- Silverstein 先生吗?  - 是的, 你是谁?

2
00:00:13,667 --> 00:00:16,227
Anne Travers. Is my father here?
Anne Travers．我父亲在这里吗?

3
00:00:16,387 --> 00:00:20,619
Yes, he's here. Come and see him and take him away.
是的, 他在这儿．来看一下, 把他带走吧

4
00:00:20,787 --> 00:00:22,778
He's a fool. An old fool!
他糊涂了, 老糊涂了

5
00:00:22,947 --> 00:00:25,461
Father?
父亲？

6
00:00:26,707 --> 00:00:28,698
Father...
父亲...

7
00:00:29,627 --> 00:00:31,618
Anne...

8
00:00:32,387 --> 00:00:35,663
- What are you doing here?
- Looking for you.
- 你在这里做什么？   - 找你啊

9
00:00:36,787 --> 00:00:39,176
You were supposed to be meeting me.
你原本应该去接我

10
00:00:39,867 --> 00:00:42,779
- Was I?   - At the airport.
- 是吗？    - 在机场

11
00:00:43,867 --> 00:00:47,940
What's wrong? You send me a cable
saying you're in grave trouble.
怎么了？你给我发了电报说你遇到大麻烦了

12
00:00:48,107 --> 00:00:51,622
- I fly half the way round the world...
- Trouble? Yes.
- 我飞了大半个地球...   - 麻烦? 是的

13
00:00:51,787 --> 00:00:55,905
A great deal of trouble. It's that thing.
很大的麻烦．是那个东西

14
00:00:56,587 --> 00:00:58,578
- The Yeti?   - Mm.
- 雪怪？      - 嗯

15
00:00:58,747 --> 00:01:02,023
You're a stupid old fool, Julius Silverstein!
你是个愚蠢的糊涂蛋, Julius Silverstein！

16
00:01:02,187 --> 00:01:07,181
ME the fool? You would like me to be the fool
and give you back my Yeti, huh?
我是糊涂蛋？你就期望我是糊涂蛋, 好把雪怪还给你, 哈？

17
00:01:07,347 --> 00:01:10,737
You must, man. Don't you understand?
It's dangerous.
你必须, 伙计．你不明白吗？它太危险了

18
00:01:10,907 --> 00:01:16,425
For 30 years this stands here in my museum,
and now he tells me it is dangerous!
在我的博物馆放了３０年, 现在你跟我说它很危险！

19
00:01:16,587 --> 00:01:20,978
- I wish I'd never brought it back from Tibet.
- Father, what has happened?
- 我期望我没有把它从西藏带回来   - 父亲, 发生了什么？

20
00:01:21,147 --> 00:01:25,584
The silly old goat won't listen to me.
I've told him, warned him.
这头老笨山羊不听我的．我告诉他了, 警告他了

21
00:01:25,747 --> 00:01:30,662
- Damn it, he knows it's a robot!
- But, Father, the Yeti isn't dangerous.
- 蛋, 他知道这就是个机器人   - 但是, 父亲, 雪怪并不危险

22
00:01:30,827 --> 00:01:33,864
It can't work unless it has a control unit.
没有那个控制器它是不会启动的

23
00:01:34,027 --> 00:01:36,302
But I've done it, Anne!
但我搞定了, Anne！

24
00:01:36,467 --> 00:01:38,856
I HAVE reactivated the control unit.
我已经重新激活了控制器

25
00:01:39,947 --> 00:01:42,541
But, Father, this is wonderful news.
啊, 父亲, 这是非常好的消息啊

26
00:01:42,707 --> 00:01:46,177
Is it? Yes, I suppose it would be,
except for one thing.
是吗？是, 我也觉得是, 除了一件事

27
00:01:46,347 --> 00:01:48,338
What?
什么？

28
00:01:48,507 --> 00:01:50,304
The sphere - it's gone!
那个球  - 不见了！

29
00:01:50,467 --> 00:01:54,699
It's disappeared! You must let me
have the Yeti back, Julius.
它小时了！你必须得让我把雪怪要回来, Julius

30
00:01:56,947 --> 00:01:58,744
Make him understand, Anne!
你跟他说明白吧, Anne!

31
00:01:58,907 --> 00:02:00,898
I understand.
我很明白

32
00:02:01,067 --> 00:02:03,740
I buy the Yeti off you 30 years ago.
我30年前从你手里买走了雪怪

33
00:02:03,907 --> 00:02:06,501
Now, it is valuable.
现在, 它值钱了

34
00:02:06,667 --> 00:02:10,057
You try to scare me, take your Yeti back.
你就试图吓唬吧, 好把你的雪怪要回去

35
00:02:10,227 --> 00:02:12,218
Why? Money!
为什么？钱！

36
00:02:12,387 --> 00:02:16,585
- You want to rob me!
- I'll buy the thing back if that's what you want!
- 你想抢劫我！   - 我可以把它买回来, 如果你想要的是这个

37
00:02:17,587 --> 00:02:20,659
No, no. It's priceless.
不, 不, 它是无价的

38
00:02:20,827 --> 00:02:23,580
The only one in the world, and it is mine.
全世界独一无二的, 就我才有

39
00:02:23,747 --> 00:02:25,544
- You fool!  - Thief!
- 你糊涂！    - 小偷！

40
00:02:25,707 --> 00:02:28,016
- I'm not a thief.   - Swindler!
- 我不是小偷      - 骗子！

41
00:02:28,187 --> 00:02:29,540
Stubborn old goat!
顽固的老山羊！

42
00:02:29,707 --> 00:02:33,256
- Father!   - Take him away - out of my house!
- 父亲！   - 把他带走, 离开我的房子！

43
00:02:33,427 --> 00:02:35,418
Perhaps you've made a mistake.
也许是你搞错了

44
00:02:35,587 --> 00:02:40,138
You've put the sphere away
somewhere in your laboratory and forgotten it.
你把那个球放在实验室里某个地方, 然后忘了

45
00:02:40,307 --> 00:02:43,777
- You've done it before.
- No. I've looked everywhere.
- 你以前也干过这事   - 不, 我都找遍了

46
00:02:43,947 --> 00:02:47,986
Let's go home and look again, shall we?
You know what you're like.
我们回家去, 再找找, 行吗？我知道你是怎样的

47
00:02:48,147 --> 00:02:49,500
Yes, but suppose...
好, 不过要是...

48
00:02:49,667 --> 00:02:53,740
Let's go and have a quiet dinner,
and you can tell me all about it.
走吧, 一起安静地用个晚餐, 你跟我详细说说

49
00:02:53,907 --> 00:02:56,580
Then we'll go home and look for the sphere.
然后我们回家, 找那个球

50
00:02:57,627 --> 00:03:01,222
Well, all right...
But I warned you, Julius! I warned you!
好, 行吧...但我警告过你了, Julius! 我警告过你了

51
00:03:01,387 --> 00:03:03,059
Get out! Take him away!
出去！把他带走！

52
00:03:03,227 --> 00:03:07,106
Nobody destroys Julius Silverstein's collection!
Nobody!
没谁能破坏 Julius Silverstein 的收藏品！没谁！

53
00:03:07,267 --> 00:03:09,542
- Come on, Father.
- The Yeti's mine!
- 得啦, 父亲   - 雪怪是我的！

54
00:03:09,707 --> 00:03:12,267
You can't scare me with your mad stories.
你别想用你的疯狂故事吓住我

55
00:03:13,347 --> 00:03:15,497
Out! Out!
出去！出去！

56
00:03:46,907 --> 00:03:49,341
Travers...

57
00:03:49,507 --> 00:03:53,056
It is you? I am not frightened
by your stupid tricks!
是你吗？我不会被你的愚蠢伎俩吓倒的

58
00:03:53,227 --> 00:03:55,218
Travers! I know it's you.
Travers! 我知道是你

59
00:03:55,387 --> 00:03:56,740
I'm not a fool!
我可不糊涂！

60
00:04:24,427 --> 00:04:26,179
Agh!
啊！

61
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:48,000
(theme)

62
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:53,000
<b>The Web of Fear</b>
<b>Doctor Who 1963 05x05 (whopix fan edit)</b>
<b>神秘博士老版 第五季第五集 恐惧之网 （粉丝剪辑版）</b>

63
00:05:10,087 --> 00:05:12,078
Some sort of grille.
某种栅栏

64
00:05:12,247 --> 00:05:14,681
Don't say you've landed us in a prison!
可别说你降落到了一座监狱里！

65
00:05:14,847 --> 00:05:17,156
It could be the dungeons of a castle.
可能是一座城堡的地牢

66
00:05:17,327 --> 00:05:18,680
It's so dark.
好黑呀

67
00:05:18,847 --> 00:05:20,838
Ah, steps.
啊, 台阶

68
00:05:21,007 --> 00:05:23,316
Come along. Be careful.
过来, 小心点

69
00:05:31,087 --> 00:05:32,805
Yes...
好...

70
00:05:32,967 --> 00:05:34,958
It seems to be a large room.
看起来是个很大的房间

71
00:05:35,127 --> 00:05:37,118
Tiled walls.
瓷砖墙

72
00:05:37,287 --> 00:05:39,278
Curved ceiling.
拱形天花板

73
00:05:39,447 --> 00:05:41,358
Come on.
快来

74
00:05:46,047 --> 00:05:48,038
The floor seems to end here.
地面好像到这里就没有了

75
00:05:48,207 --> 00:05:51,916
There's a sort of trench. Look.
这里有某种壕沟, 你看

76
00:05:52,087 --> 00:05:56,524
- Hey, Doctor. Come and look at this.
- What have you found, Victoria?
- 嘿, 博士, 来看看这个   - 你发现了什么, Victoria？

77
00:05:56,687 --> 00:05:58,678
See for yourself.
你自己看看

78
00:06:01,367 --> 00:06:04,677
"Covent... Garden... "
"科文特...花园..."
<i>（注：伦敦西部一街区名称, 特色是
皇家歌剧院和诸多的小商店）</i>

79
00:06:04,847 --> 00:06:10,285
Yes, of course! It's an underground station.
We're standing on the platform.
是了, 当然！这是一个地下车站, 我们站在月台上

80
00:06:10,447 --> 00:06:13,280
- Underground station?   - Underground trains.
- 地下车站？   - 地铁

81
00:06:13,447 --> 00:06:17,486
- A little after your time, Victoria.
- Is it always as dark as this?
- 略晚于你的时代, Victoria  - 总是这么黑吗？

82
00:06:17,647 --> 00:06:22,243
No, it's probably the middle of the night.
Come on. Let's go up top.
不．只是现在很可能是午夜．快来, 我们到顶上去

83
00:06:25,327 --> 00:06:30,655
- Professor Travers is here, sir.
- Why have I been brought here? Who are you?
- Travers 教授来了, 先生  - 为什么带我来这儿？你是谁？

84
00:06:30,727 --> 00:06:32,404
- Knight.       - Never heard of you.
- 我叫 Knight   - 从没听说过

85
00:06:32,567 --> 00:06:34,558
Captain Knight. OK, Corporal.
Knight 上校。好了, 下士

86
00:06:35,607 --> 00:06:37,484
It's no good shouting at me.
朝我喊可没什么好处

87
00:06:37,647 --> 00:06:40,036
- I didn't ask for you.   - Who did, then?
- 不是我叫你来的   - 那是谁？

88
00:06:40,207 --> 00:06:43,722
- Your daughter.
- Anne? Just like her mother.
- 你女儿   - Anne? 真像她妈

89
00:06:43,887 --> 00:06:45,798
Always interfering in things she knows nothing about!
总是在她啥也不懂的事情上插手

90
00:06:45,967 --> 00:06:48,925
I understood that you'd sent for her
to come back from America to help you.
我还以为是你把她从美国叫回来帮你的

91
00:06:49,087 --> 00:06:50,725
What do you want me for, anyway?
你要我做什么？

92
00:06:50,887 --> 00:06:53,360
I don't. I consider this to be a military matter./
不是我要。我认为这是一个军事问题

93
00:06:53,833 --> 00:06:57,360
Well, you haven't much success so far, haven you?
那你到目前也还没获得什么成功, 是吧？

94
00:07:01,607 --> 00:07:05,361
Army? What the devil do they know about it?
军方？他们到底对这个知道些什么？

95
00:07:09,687 --> 00:07:13,805
- The Doctor was wrong!
- It's not night-time. It's broad daylight.
- 博士搞错了！   - 现在不是晚上, 是光天白日

96
00:07:16,007 --> 00:07:20,797
- Just let me get my breath... Those stairs!
- It looks like we're locked in.
- 且让我喘口气...这些台阶！   - 看来我们被锁在里面了

97
00:07:20,967 --> 00:07:22,878
- That's strange.  - Doctor...
- 这很奇怪啊     - 博士...

98
00:07:23,047 --> 00:07:25,561
- Yes?    - Listen.
- 什么？   - 听

99
00:07:25,727 --> 00:07:27,240
I can't hear anything.
我什么也没听到

100
00:07:28,847 --> 00:07:31,720
Oh... It IS quiet. I see what you mean./
噢...是太安静了．我明白你的意思了

101
00:07:31,850 --> 00:07:35,320
The middle of London. There should be some noise.
伦敦市中心, 应该会有些噪音才对

102
00:07:35,487 --> 00:07:38,240
Hey, Doctor. There's an old man over there. Let's ask him.
嘿，博士，那儿有个老人, 我们去问问他

103
00:07:38,407 --> 00:07:40,318
Yes, go on.
对, 去吧

104
00:07:42,487 --> 00:07:44,159
Excuse me...
打扰一下...

105
00:07:45,327 --> 00:07:47,318
Excuse me...
打扰一下...

106
00:07:51,047 --> 00:07:52,644
Who are you?
你是谁？

107
00:07:52,707 --> 00:07:55,516
- Harold Chorley. London Television.
- Oh, What? 
- Harold Chorley. 伦敦电视台   - 噢，什么？

108
00:07:55,587 --> 00:07:58,126
Television? Never watch it. Are you an actor or something?
电视台？从来没看过．你是个演员什么的吗？

109
00:07:59,401 --> 00:08:01,226
Journalist, actually.
新闻记者, 实际上

110
00:08:01,687 --> 00:08:06,884
The government decided to only allow one
correspondent down here. The press chose me.
政府决定允许派一个新闻记者下来, 台里选了我

111
00:08:07,347 --> 00:08:08,724
Oh, yeah?
噢, 那又怎样？

112
00:08:09,487 --> 00:08:14,677
Tell me, Professor, will you be in charge
of the scientific section, or will your daughter?
告诉我，教授，是你负责这里的科学组吗？还是你女儿

113
00:08:14,847 --> 00:08:16,838
Mind your own business!
管好你自己的事！

114
00:08:17,687 --> 00:08:21,700
How long do you think it will take you
to come up with the answer?
你觉得你需要多久才能得到答案？

115
00:08:21,767 --> 00:08:25,482
- One week? Three, perhaps?
- How the hell should I know?
- 一周？三周, 也许要？  - 我怎么可能知道？

116
00:08:25,647 --> 00:08:27,478
- Is that working?
- Of course.
- 那东西好使吗？   - 当然

117
00:08:28,467 --> 00:08:30,860
It's more than likely
we may not be able to defeat this menace.
感觉更像是, 我们可能无法消除这场危机

118
00:08:30,927 --> 00:08:37,303
London...the whole of England might be completely
wiped out. There - did you get that?
伦敦...整个英格兰都可能被完全毁灭．喏 - 你明白了吗？

119
00:08:59,627 --> 00:09:02,699
- What are you doing?
- Just confirming something.
- 你要干什么去？  - 去确认点事情

120
00:09:02,867 --> 00:09:06,985
Just as I thought.
There haven't been any trains here for some time.
正如我说料, 这里有段时间没跑地铁了

121
00:09:07,147 --> 00:09:09,138
What's that over there?
那边是什么？

122
00:09:14,947 --> 00:09:19,020
It's a power cable.
I wonder what it's doing down here.
是一根电缆．我很好奇它在这里有什么用

123
00:09:19,187 --> 00:09:21,178
In there quickly!
进去那儿, 快！

124
00:09:55,187 --> 00:09:58,463
Soldiers? I wonder what they're doing down here.
士兵？奇怪, 他们在这下面干什么？

125
00:09:58,627 --> 00:10:03,098
- Let's go and ask them.
- No. I think we'd better tread carefully.
- 我们去问问他们   - 不, 我觉得我们还是小心行事

126
00:10:03,267 --> 00:10:06,020
Let's go and find out what's going on first.
我们去看看是在干什么

127
00:10:14,947 --> 00:10:17,017
What do you want us to do, Doctor?
你期望我们做什么, 博士？

128
00:10:17,187 --> 00:10:20,782
You follow the soldiers, but keep out of sight.
你跟着那些士兵, 但别被看见了

129
00:10:20,947 --> 00:10:22,567
I'm going to see where this cable goes to./
我要去看看这些线缆通向那里

130
00:10:22,700 --> 00:10:25,567
Meet back here in a few minutes. Right？
过几分钟回来这里汇合。好吧？

131
00:10:36,587 --> 00:10:39,545
- What's the matter?
- I thought I heard something.
- 怎么了？   - 我觉得我听到了点什么

132
00:10:39,707 --> 00:10:44,144
- Getting a bit jumpy, aren't you, Weams?
- It's no wonder, is it, Staff?
- 有点神经质了吧, 是不, Weams?  - 那也不稀奇, 是吧, Staff?

133
00:10:44,307 --> 00:10:48,061
- Shall we connect the new drum now, Staff?
- All right, Corporal.
- 我们现在连上新鼓吗, Staff (FIXME)
- 好的, 下士

134
00:10:49,467 --> 00:10:52,186
- Good thing we fixed these lights.  - Yeah.
- 好的是我们把这些灯修好了  - 是啊

135
00:10:58,387 --> 00:11:01,982
- I can't hear anything.
- Are they still there?
- 我什么也听不见   - 他们还在那儿吗？

136
00:11:02,147 --> 00:11:04,980
I think they must be moving. Come on.
我觉得他们肯定走了．快来

137
00:11:06,507 --> 00:11:08,225
Agh!
啊！

138
00:11:10,907 --> 00:11:14,183
- I told you I heard something, didn't I?  - Yeah.
- 我就说我听到了什么, 说过吧   - 是

139
00:11:14,347 --> 00:11:16,258
Come on!
快点！

140
00:11:16,427 --> 00:11:19,066
- I'm sorry!   - It was only a cobweb!
- 我很抱歉！   - 不过是蜘蛛网

141
00:11:19,227 --> 00:11:23,266
- Do you think they heard?
- Hope not. Come on.
- 你觉得他们听到了吗？   - 但愿没有, 快来

142
00:11:33,387 --> 00:11:37,221
Well, well, well, would you believe it?
The Babes in the Wood!
好, 好, 好, 你能相信不？树林中的美女! (FIXME)

143
00:13:05,127 --> 00:13:09,598
- You're quite sure there was nobody with you?
- How many more times?
- 你确定你们没有其他人？   - 还要说多少次？

144
00:13:09,767 --> 00:13:11,564
That's all right, then.
那就没事了

145
00:13:12,887 --> 00:13:16,197
- Clear to fire, Staff?
- Yes, they were on their own.
- 可以点火了吗, Staff?   - 是的, 就他们自己

146
00:13:16,367 --> 00:13:18,358
Right.
好

147
00:13:18,527 --> 00:13:20,518
What was all that about?
这都是怎么回事？

148
00:13:21,567 --> 00:13:25,640
I suppose there's no harm in telling you.
You two are very lucky.
我觉得告诉你也没有关系, 你们俩非常幸运

149
00:13:25,807 --> 00:13:28,560
- We're going to blow up the tunnel.
- What?!
- 我们打算炸掉这个隧道   - 什么?!

150
00:13:28,727 --> 00:13:31,366
- That's what the cable's for.
- The Doctor!
- 那些电缆是干这个的   - 博士！

151
